	<h2>Inspection Procedure</h2>		
	<ul>
	    <li>1. Inspecting officers are required to feed the monthly/annual inspection summary templates to be prescribed in this behalf for uploading in the public domain with the help of computer program prepared by any authorised agency.</li>
	    <li>nspecting Officers must upload their inspection reports in the prescribed inspection proforma within 72 hours of inspection.(Refer to Annexure-A in the notifications).(<a href="<?php echo $server_url; ?>dept_documents/cei/notifications/Factory Notifications.pdf" target="_blank"> <i class="fa fa-file-pdf-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> Factory Notifications.pdf</a>)</li>
	    <li>3. There will be a computerised generation of inspection program and  communication to the inspecting officers.</li>
	    <li>4. In the interest of making the factory inspection more efficient, transparent, accountable and to avoid duplicity of inspection, inspection by the Senior Inspector of Factories should be of the  nature of monitoring and supervising the effectiveness and quality of inspection by the Inspector of Factories and compliance status in addition to their normal independent inspection.</li>
	    <li>5. Mandatory inspection will be done as per requirement outlined in the notifications.For more information click on hyperlink (<a href="<?php echo $server_url; ?>dept_documents/cei/notifications/Factory Notifications.pdf" target="_blank"> <i class="fa fa-file-pdf-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> Factory Notifications.pdf</a>) and refer to Annexure -4</li>
	    <li>6. Optional inspection would be undertaken once a year or as per requirement subject to permission from head of offices.</li>
	</ul>
	<h2>Inspection Guidelines</h2>		
	<ul>
	    <li>1. The Inspector should visit the site on pre selected date</li>
	    <li>2. Inspecting Officers must upload their inspection reports in the prescribed inspection proforma within 72 hours of inspection.(Refer to Annexure-A in the notifications). (<a href="<?php echo $server_url; ?>dept_documents/cei/notifications/Factory Notifications.pdf" target="_blank"> <i class="fa fa-file-pdf-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> Factory Notifications.pdf</a>)</li>
	    <li>3. Mandatory inspection will be done as per requirement.</li>
	    <li>4. Optional inspection would be undertaken once a year or as per requirement subject to permission from head of offices.</li>
	    <li>5. There will be a computerised generation of inspection program and communication to the inspecting officers.</li>
	    <li>6. The applicant should keep the physical copies of all the documents ready on the inspection day.</li>
	</ul>
